	-> Battle
		âœ…ï¸ Battle happens when a player is adjacent to the other orthogonally after moving.
			âœ…ï¸ If a battle happens on the last move of the turn, the turn only ends after the battle.
			âœ…ï¸ (Bonus) Diagonal battles.
		âœ…ï¸ The battle is decided over auto dice roll.
			âœ…ï¸ Players have dices of different colors (blue x red).
		âœ…ï¸ Each dice is six-sided.
			(Bonus) Different dices (twelve-sided, ten-sided etc).
		âœ…ï¸ Each player rolls 3 dices.
			âœ…ï¸ Battle is resolved by comparing pairs of dices between players, ordered by their value with higher coming first.
				(5, 6, 2) X (5, 4, 3)
				6 X 5
				5 X 4
				2 X 3
				(5, 6, 2) wins.
		âœ…ï¸ If the values are the same the turn player wins the comparison.
		âœ…ï¸ The player with more individual dice wins, wins the battle.
			The loser suffers damage to their health points equal to the winnerâ€™s attack power.
